{
  "toolbox_name": "XiaoZhi AI",
  "toolbox_labels": {
    "说明:小智事件中禁用delay阻塞编程，简单定时器不如多线程": "Note: Disable delay blocking programming in Xiaozhi events. Simple timers are not as good as multi-threads.",
    "说明:1. 预内置和自定义不可混用": "Note: 1. Pre-built-in and customized cannot be mixed.",
    "   2. 自定义需要自己画界面,内容可自定，灵活但麻烦": "2. Customization requires you to draw the interface yourself, and the content can be customized, which is flexible but troublesome.",
    "   3. 预内置是定死的，但直接可用": "3. The pre-built-in is fixed, but can be used directly.",
    "*特别声明1. 屏显功能需要加载LVGL库": "*Special statement 1. The screen display function needs to load the LVGL library",
    "*特别声明2. 在LVGL库初始化中需‘设置图像字体开启’": "*Special statement 2. It is necessary to ‘set image font on’ during LVGL library initialization",
    "*特别声明3. 需自绘界面的，一般用TFT_eSPI库，按例程": "*Special statement 3. If you need to draw your own interface, generally use the TFT_eSPI library and follow the routine",
    " 就行，这里的自定义一般不需要，单色屏时可考虑使用": "That’s fine. Customization here is generally not needed. You can consider using it when using a monochrome screen.",
    "说明:操作设备代码放设置，服务器读取代码放上报": "Description: The operating device code is set, and the server reads the code and reports it."
  },
